for business.

38
00:02:02,788 --> 00:02:04,792
Okay, what if I say,

39
00:02:04,826 --> 00:02:08,036
«Bonnie, my girlfriend,
<i>your</i> real estate agent»?

40
00:02:08,070 --> 00:02:09,773
— Nice to meet you.
