technological advancement?

108
00:05:59,733 --> 00:06:01,666
I think that's worse than
being late, isn't it?

109
00:06:01,701 --> 00:06:03,868
You're right.
Good thinking.

110
00:06:03,903 --> 00:06:06,269
Maybe later, off campus.

111
