160
00:08:56,040 --> 00:08:57,742
Lou?

161
00:08:57,776 --> 00:09:00,607
I think Peggy
is the right choice.

162
00:09:02,375 --> 00:09:04,374
Well, I'm glad all agree the
client is going to love

163
00:09:04,408 --> 00:09:05,808
having a woman's
point of view--

164
00:09:05,843 --> 00:09:07,744
