it be family.

212
00:11:15,243 --> 00:11:17,941
If you don't want to do it, I've got
a long list of strangers I can pay.

213
00:11:17,975 --> 00:11:19,873
You're upset.

214
00:11:19,907 --> 00:11:22,844
You're not thinking right.

215
00:11:22,878 --> 00:11:25,677
