don't tell us what happened.

216
00:11:30,180 --> 00:11:32,982
Look, she hasn't
been herself lately

217
00:11:33,016 --> 00:11:36,485
and we went to this
marriage encounter group.

218
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:38,287
( chuckles )
