to talk to people.

221
00:11:41,792 --> 00:11:43,192
That's always a mistake.

222
00:11:43,227 --> 00:11:45,828
Roger!

223
00:11:45,862 --> 00:11:48,332
Brooks, sweetheart,

224
00:11:48,366 --> 00:11:50,532
I don't mind watching
my grandson,

225
00:11:50,566 --> 00:11:52,100
but it sounds like
you tried to stop her

226
00:11:52,134 --> 00:11:54,104
and you obviously failed.

227
00:11:54,138 --> 00:11:57,210
— A father is a powerful thing.
— What are you doing?

228
00:11:57,244 --> 00:11:59,378
Of course, she'll watch him.
Let the man be a man.

229
00:12:01,079 --> 00:12:03,348
I appreciate that, sir.
I'm gonna go say goodbye.

230
00:12:03,382 --> 00:12:06,348
