You know you never have to
have another drink again.

766
00:42:31,413 --> 00:42:33,314
I don't want to hear
that right now.

767
00:42:33,349 --> 00:42:35,416
You're hungover. It's the
best time to hear it.

768
00:42:37,119 --> 00:42:39,420
I mean, are you
just going to kill yourself?

769
00:42:39,454 --> 00:42:41,755
Give them what they want?

770
00:42:41,790 --> 00:42:44,691
Or go in your bedroom,
get in uniform,

771
00:42:44,726 --> 00:42:48,061
fix your bayonet,
and hit the parade?

772
00:42:49,096 --> 00:42:50,930
Do the work, Don.

773
