Where's my daughter?

776
00:43:12,985 --> 00:43:15,854
She's probably at the
creek getting water.

777
00:43:15,888 --> 00:43:17,156
I don't think so.

778
00:43:18,759 --> 00:43:21,764
It's a beautiful night
and a beautiful morning.

779
00:43:22,900 --> 00:43:24,234
Did you see the sunrise?

780
00:43:29,341 --> 00:43:31,576
It's a beautiful
morning, isn't it?

781
00:43:31,610 --> 00:43:33,278
It's time to leave
Shangri-La, baby.

782
00:43:33,312 --> 00:43:35,781
Take a good look, say
goodbye to your friends.

783
00:43:35,815 --> 00:43:37,783
You were doing so well, Daddy.

784
00:43:37,817 --> 00:43:39,552
Fine, you don't want to say goodbye?
Let's go.

785
00:43:39,586 --> 00:43:42,255
Hey, man, leave her be.

786
